WEBVTT

00:01:11.905 --> 00:01:14.741
♪ look at the stars

00:01:14.866 --> 00:01:18.870
♪ look how they shine for you

00:01:20.622 --> 00:01:23.625
♪ and everything you do

00:01:26.044 --> 00:01:28.630
♪ yeah, they were all yellow

00:01:28.755 --> 00:01:31.341
♪ I came along

00:01:31.466 --> 00:01:32.968
♪ I wrote a song for you... ♪

00:01:33.093 --> 00:01:34.928
hey, love bug. You ready?

00:01:35.053 --> 00:01:37.639
- Yeah. Hey, guess what, mum.
- What?

00:01:37.764 --> 00:01:41.101
- I figured out where wasps come from.
- Oh, yeah? Where?

00:01:41.226 --> 00:01:46.064
Well, I think it must be
if you flick a rock into the airjust right,

00:01:46.189 --> 00:01:47.691
it'll turn into a wasp.

00:01:47.816 --> 00:01:49.651
- Dang!
- Yep.

00:01:49.776 --> 00:01:50.902
That's cool.

00:01:51.737 --> 00:01:53.488
So, how was your day at school?

00:01:53.614 --> 00:01:55.282
Fine.

00:01:55.407 --> 00:01:57.510
Yeah, I had a good meeting
with miss Butler this time.

00:01:57.534 --> 00:01:59.620
- I kinda liked her.
- What did she say?

00:01:59.745 --> 00:02:03.165
Well, she said that you weren't turning in
your homework assignments.

00:02:03.290 --> 00:02:06.126
And I told her, "I know he does 'em
cos I check 'em every night."

00:02:06.251 --> 00:02:10.172
She said she found a big chunk of 'em
crumpled up at the bottom of your backpack.

00:02:10.297 --> 00:02:11.798
She didn't ask for 'em.

00:02:11.923 --> 00:02:14.643
Well, baby, she doesn't have to.
You're just supposed to turn 'em in.

00:02:15.719 --> 00:02:18.430
And she said you're still
staring out the window all day.

00:02:19.056 --> 00:02:21.308
Not all day.

00:02:21.433 --> 00:02:24.186
And she said that you destroyed
her pencil sharpener.

00:02:24.311 --> 00:02:26.188
Not on purpose.

00:02:26.313 --> 00:02:28.482
Wait, she said that you crammed
a bunch of rocks in it.

00:02:29.066 --> 00:02:32.277
I thought if it can sharpen pencils,
maybe it could sharpen rocks.

00:02:34.196 --> 00:02:36.948
Well, what were you gonna do
with a bunch of sharpened rocks?

00:02:37.407 --> 00:02:40.327
I was trying to make arrowheads
for my rock collection.

00:02:42.329 --> 00:02:43.747
Hmm.

00:03:02.891 --> 00:03:05.977
- Dude, it's my turn!
- Hold on.

00:03:17.823 --> 00:03:20.325
Mason!

00:03:21.618 --> 00:03:22.869
Samantha!

00:03:23.829 --> 00:03:26.665
Oh! Tommy. Is Mason down there?

00:03:26.790 --> 00:03:27.999
Yeah.

00:03:28.125 --> 00:03:30.961
Well, tell him he has
to come home for dinner.

00:03:31.086 --> 00:03:32.546
Ok.

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:41.221
'Where do you think you're going?
Wait. Come back here.'

00:03:45.684 --> 00:03:47.769
- Hey.
- Hey, sweetie.

00:03:47.894 --> 00:03:49.563
Why aren't you ready?

00:03:50.230 --> 00:03:53.233
- Hey, Mason.
- Hey, Ted.

00:03:53.358 --> 00:03:55.294
- Come on, come on. Hurry up. Let's go.
- What time is it?

00:03:55.318 --> 00:03:56.518
It's nine. Let's go, let's go.

00:03:56.611 --> 00:03:58.613
Ok, I meant to call you
cos Janice flaked out.

00:03:58.739 --> 00:04:01.491
- I don't have a sitter.
- Why didn't you call somebody else?

00:04:01.616 --> 00:04:03.952
Well, I can't get a babysitter now.
It's nine o'clock.

00:04:04.077 --> 00:04:05.912
But you're welcome
to hang out with us.

00:04:06.037 --> 00:04:09.875
Well, no. I mean, we have plans.
The guys are expecting me.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.753
- Well, you can go.
- All right.

00:04:12.878 --> 00:04:15.130
Yeah, well, I'll come back
in a couple of hours.

00:04:15.255 --> 00:04:17.340
Is that ok?

00:04:17.466 --> 00:04:20.469
- Yeah. Yes. It's ok.
- All right.

00:04:24.347 --> 00:04:26.266
"'Turn back! Turn back!

00:04:26.391 --> 00:04:28.226
"'I don't wanna talk to moaning myrtle.'

00:04:28.351 --> 00:04:30.687
"'who?' said Harry
as they backtracked quickly.

00:04:30.812 --> 00:04:35.400
"'She haunts one of the toilets in the girls
bathroom on the first floor, ' said Hermione.

00:04:35.525 --> 00:04:37.277
"'She haunts a toilet?'

00:04:37.402 --> 00:04:39.070
"'yes, it's been out of order all year

00:04:39.196 --> 00:04:42.282
"'because she keeps having tantrums
and flooding the place.

00:04:42.407 --> 00:04:44.409
