if I could avoid it.

00:04:44.534 --> 00:04:47.370
"'It's awful trying to have a pee
with her wailing at you.'"

00:04:47.496 --> 00:04:49.414
Why can't you just say that?

00:04:49.539 --> 00:04:51.642
- I'm sorry. I don't wanna go with you.
- You're sorry! That's bullshit!

00:04:51.666 --> 00:04:53.352
That's right.
I wanna stay here with my kids.

00:04:53.376 --> 00:04:54.416
That's what I'd rather do.

00:04:54.503 --> 00:04:56.755
Would you stop using your kids
as an excuse?

00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:58.632
I'm not using my kids
as an excuse!

00:04:58.757 --> 00:05:01.593
You don't even know.
You have this immature life.

00:05:01.718 --> 00:05:03.654
- You have no responsibilities.
- I have an immature life?

00:05:03.678 --> 00:05:05.198
- I have responsibilities.
- I have an immature life?

00:05:05.222 --> 00:05:06.824
You don't know
what it's like to be a parent.

00:05:06.848 --> 00:05:10.393
No, I don't! And why am I responsible
for your mistakes in life?

00:05:10.519 --> 00:05:12.854
Don't call my kids mistakes!
Don't!

00:05:12.979 --> 00:05:14.064
I didn't call your kids...

00:05:14.189 --> 00:05:18.151
You said, "you're respons... your mistakes
in your life," pointing at my kids.

00:05:18.276 --> 00:05:22.280
This is the reality. I am a parent!
That means responsibility.

00:05:22.405 --> 00:05:25.200
I would love to have some time
to myself!

00:05:25.325 --> 00:05:27.077
I would love to just go
to a fuckin' movie!

00:05:27.202 --> 00:05:30.705
You don't think I'd like that?
Go have some dinner, go to a bar?

00:05:30.831 --> 00:05:32.183
I don't even know what that's like.

00:05:32.207 --> 00:05:35.210
I was someone's daughter,
then I was somebody's fucking mother!

00:05:35.335 --> 00:05:36.962
Ok? I don't know what that's like.

00:05:39.381 --> 00:05:41.800
♪ oops, I did it again

00:05:41.925 --> 00:05:44.845
♪ I played with your heart,
got lost in the game

00:05:44.970 --> 00:05:45.971
♪ oh, baby, baby

00:05:46.096 --> 00:05:48.265
♪ oops, you think I'm in love

00:05:48.390 --> 00:05:51.017
♪ I was sent from above

00:05:51.142 --> 00:05:53.311
- ♪ I'm not that innocent...
- Stop!

00:05:54.062 --> 00:05:55.498
- Quit it!
- ♪ you see, my problem is this

00:05:55.522 --> 00:05:57.232
♪ I'm dreaming away

00:05:57.357 --> 00:05:59.484
- ♪ wishing that heroes truly exist...
- Quit it!

00:05:59.609 --> 00:06:02.028
♪ I cry, watching the days

00:06:02.153 --> 00:06:04.072
