00:06:14.249 --> 00:06:17.252
Mason, do not throw things
at your sister.

00:06:17.377 --> 00:06:19.170
She's faking. She hit me first.

00:06:19.296 --> 00:06:21.882
Listen, both of you.
I'm going back to bed.

00:06:22.007 --> 00:06:24.207
I don't wanna hear another peep
out of here for an hour.

00:06:24.301 --> 00:06:25.343
Go to sleep.

00:06:29.472 --> 00:06:31.558
- Faker!
- Hey!

00:06:45.155 --> 00:06:47.157
Oh!

00:06:47.282 --> 00:06:50.243
Look at that.
Found it in the street.

00:06:50.368 --> 00:06:52.370
Dude!

00:06:54.706 --> 00:06:55.957
I know, right?

00:06:56.082 --> 00:06:58.335
Look at those.

00:06:58.460 --> 00:07:01.880
Ooh. Look at those!

00:07:03.423 --> 00:07:04.591
Oh!

00:07:20.357 --> 00:07:22.943
So listen, guys, I wanna talk to you
about something.

00:07:23.068 --> 00:07:26.237
And you might not like this idea at first,
but we're moving to Houston.

00:07:27.697 --> 00:07:29.950
- When?
- Vveh, soon.

00:07:30.075 --> 00:07:32.970
