and all around the doorways on the inside.

00:09:20.226 --> 00:09:24.814
She says we're gonna come visit,
and I'm gonna write and call you.

00:09:26.232 --> 00:09:29.277
Oh, wait, hold on a second.
I'm getting another call.

00:09:30.195 --> 00:09:31.696
Hello?

00:09:32.363 --> 00:09:34.741
Sorry, Tommy.
Mason can't come over today.

00:09:34.866 --> 00:09:35.950
We're moving.

00:09:36.076 --> 00:09:39.037
And I'm on the other line. Bye.

00:09:39.788 --> 00:09:41.956
Althea?

00:09:42.082 --> 00:09:45.502
I'm gonna be sending
the scout instructions.

00:09:45.627 --> 00:09:49.631
Email and write back telling me
how the other scouts are doing.

00:09:50.673 --> 00:09:53.760
Well, because you're the leader now.

00:09:55.345 --> 00:09:58.181
Ok, let's go, cos I wanna get there
before it gets dark.

00:09:58.306 --> 00:10:01.643
Goodbye, yard. Goodbye, crape myrtle.
Goodbye, mailbox.

00:10:01.768 --> 00:10:06.106
Goodbye, box of stuff mummy won't let us
take with us, but we don't wanna throw away.

00:10:06.231 --> 00:10:10.318
Goodbye, house. I'll never like mummy
