00:10:10.443 --> 00:10:11.611
Samantha!

00:10:11.736 --> 00:10:14.489
Why don't you say goodbye
to that little horseshit attitude, ok?

00:10:14.614 --> 00:10:16.699
Cos we're not taking that in the car.

00:10:16.825 --> 00:10:21.121
Goodbye, old lady who listens
