Let's do it! Go!

00:14:36.959 --> 00:14:39.504
Go? Wait a minute.
You gotta get your stuff.

00:14:39.629 --> 00:14:42.048
- Oh, yeah.
- Your backpack, your purse.

00:14:42.173 --> 00:14:43.925
Homework. Go to the bathroom.

00:14:44.050 --> 00:14:46.177
