who like presents, are you?

00:15:36.436 --> 00:15:37.687
- Yes!
- Nah! You don't.

00:15:37.812 --> 00:15:38.852
- Of course we are!
- Yeah!

00:15:38.938 --> 00:15:42.024
- Presents? Really? Let's go!
- Yay!

00:15:42.150 --> 00:15:44.670
- I call front seat!
- I wanted the front seat though.

00:15:44.694 --> 00:15:46.380
All right. Well, Mason gets it
on the way there,

00:15:46.404 --> 00:15:48.239
and Samantha gets it
on the way back, huh?

00:15:48.364 --> 00:15:50.783
- Hop in there.
- Seat belts!

