00:43:04.665 --> 00:43:06.667
- you brush your teeth?
- What?

00:43:06.793 --> 00:43:10.671
- Did you brush your teeth?
- Oh, yeah. Yeah.

00:43:10.797 --> 00:43:12.316
You gonna fall asleep
with those things in your head?

00:43:12.340 --> 00:43:13.341
Maybe.

00:43:13.466 --> 00:43:15.551
- Yeah, well, try not to, all right?
- Ok.

00:43:15.676 --> 00:43:18.096
- You want me to turn off the light?
- Sure.

00:43:18.679 --> 00:43:20.848
- Good night, Sam.
- Good night, dad.

00:43:23.184 --> 00:43:25.269
- Good night, Sam.
- Good night, Jimmy.

00:43:25.394 --> 00:43:26.813
Hey.

00:43:27.355 --> 00:43:30.316
- That was a fun day, right?
- Yeah, it was. Sorry.

00:43:31.609 --> 00:43:33.778
- Why?
- That Mason had to be there, you know?

00:43:33.903 --> 00:43:37.740
- Good night.
- Good night.

00:43:42.578 --> 00:43:43.913
Dad?

00:43:45.665 --> 00:43:51.254
There's no, like... real magic
in the world, right?

00:43:51.379 --> 00:43:52.713
What do you mean?

00:43:53.548 --> 00:43:56.884
You know, like elves and stuff.

00:43:57.009 --> 00:43:58.886
People just made that up.

00:44:00.221 --> 00:44:01.806
I don't know.

00:44:02.723 --> 00:44:05.643
I mean, what makes you think
that elves are any more magical

00:44:05.768 --> 00:44:07.812
than something like... like a whale?

00:44:09.438 --> 00:44:11.607
You know what I mean?
What if I told you a story

00:44:11.732 --> 00:44:17.905
about how underneath the ocean,
there was this giant sea mammal

00:44:18.030 --> 00:44:20.783
that used sonar and sang songs,

00:44:20.908 --> 00:44:24.829
and it was so big that its heart
was the size of a car

00:44:24.954 --> 00:44:27.790
and you could crawl
through the arteries?

00:44:27.915 --> 00:44:30.293
I mean, you'd think
that was pretty magical, right?

00:44:30.418 --> 00:44:32.837
Yeah.

00:44:32.962 --> 00:44:36.215
But, like... right this second,

00:44:36.340 --> 00:44:41.512
there's, like, no elves
in the world, right?

00:44:43.347 --> 00:44:46.434
No. Technically, no elves.

00:44:55.193 --> 00:44:57.695
♪ that you have...

00:44:57.820 --> 00:44:58.922
