- Seriously.

02:01:42.921 --> 02:01:45.215
I read this thing the other day
about how...

02:01:45.340 --> 02:01:48.092
Like, when you hear
that "ding" on your inbox,

02:01:48.218 --> 02:01:50.804
you get, like, a dopamine rush
in your brain.

02:01:50.929 --> 02:01:55.266
It's like we're being chemically rewarded
