02:01:55.391 --> 02:01:59.312
How evil is that? We're fucked.

02:01:59.437 --> 02:02:02.315
So you deleting your Facebook page
is gonna change all that?

02:02:03.608 --> 02:02:06.611
Remember when Trevor deleted
